HEADWORD: Resigned
<hw>Re*signed"</hw> <pr>(r⟦esl⟧*z⟦imac⟧nd")</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<def>Submissive; yielding; not disposed to resist or murmur.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>A firm, yet cautious mind;⟦br⟧
Sincere, though prudent; constant, yet <qex>resigned</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Pope.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Resignedly</ent>⟦br⟧
